  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Sear the shrimp until pink, about 2 minutes per side.",
    "Remove the shrimp from the pan and set aside.",
    "Add more oil if necessary, then saut\u00102 the onion and garlic until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the aji amarillo pepper and cook for 1 minute more.",
    "Add the chicken broth, coconut milk, mustard seeds, salt, black pepper, and cumin, and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add the amaranth leaves and pandan leaves to the pan, and cook for 2 minutes more.",
    "Return the shrimp to the pan and cook until heated through.",
    "Serve the chupe in pandan leaf wraps, garnished with additional amaranth leaves if desired."
